LeConte, 1847: 397. Type locality: &quot;Lacum Superiorem&quot; (original citation), herein restricted to Marquette, Marquette County, Michigan (see Hubbard and Schwarz 1878: 629). Lectotype (â™‚), designated by Noonan (1991: 108), in MCZ [# 5888].
